### --- PREVENT FOLDER BLOCKING ---
# Ensure the directory itself isn't ignored so Git can see the files inside
!spring-config/

### --- SPECIFIC ALLOW RULES ---
# These rules ensure your config files are tracked even if other YAMLs are ignored
!spring-config/application.yml
!spring-config/application-dev.yml
!spring-config/application-prod.yml

# Alternatively, keep this wildcard for any future env-specific yaml files
!spring-config/*.yml

